    "description": "在 Shadows of the Werewolf 演示版中体验电影式的恐怖冒险。面对冷酷无情的狼人，抢先感受未来的惊险内容。沉浸在紧张的氛围中，揭开完整版中等待你的黑暗秘密。你能在满月下生存下来吗？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >电影式叙事</h2> 通过沉浸式过场动画和戏剧性时刻，将恐怖、悬疑与动作的完美结合呈现给玩家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/bb4fb5661c5a46a5764bfe16877698b2.poster.avif?t=1729112160\" width=700 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/bb4fb5661c5a46a5764bfe16877698b2.webm?t=1729112160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/bb4fb5661c5a46a5764bfe16877698b2.mp4?t=1729112160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存玩法与物理引擎战斗：</h2> 隐藏、战斗或利用环境。参与动态战斗，角色和物体都根据物理引擎作出真实反应。使用有限耐久度的物品进行格挡、攻击或投掷敌人；你的每个选择都会影响战斗结果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/e7f272d72ec3c38a63a4ad45042e53c6.poster.avif?t=1729112160\" width=700 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/e7f272d72ec3c38a63a4ad45042e53c6.webm?t=1729112160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/e7f272d72ec3c38a63a4ad45042e53c6.mp4?t=1729112160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >氛围十足的环境</h2> 探索危险地点，如郊区住宅、鬼魅森林度假屋、花园迷宫等更多未知领域。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/c5fb13bfaf8cf247cb1ad207763097a8.poster.avif?t=1729112160\" width=700 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/c5fb13bfaf8cf247cb1ad207763097a8.webm?t=1729112160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/c5fb13bfaf8cf247cb1ad207763097a8.mp4?t=1729112160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >资源管理与挑战</h2> 小心管理你有限的物品库存，以在致命的遭遇中生存并解决紧张的谜题。每一件物品都至关重要，帮助你应对危险情境，并保持高强度的悬念氛围。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/a66440cfcb9a5e40f916e532f179a35f.poster.avif?t=1729112160\" width=700 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/a66440cfcb9a5e40f916e532f179a35f.webm?t=1729112160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193100/extras/a66440cfcb9a5e40f916e532f179a35f.mp4?t=1729112160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难度设置</h2> 选择简单、普通或困难模式，按照你的游戏风格调整体验。无论你是为剧情而来，还是为了终极生存挑战，都有适合每位玩家的模式。",
